 achieve higher packet delivery ratio before\nthe deadline.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Oct 2017 19:09:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Oct 2017 16:57:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-30"}
