X GPU. Additionally, we collected\nfirst of it's kind dataset for solar panel image analysis consisting 45,000+\nimages.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Oct 2017 20:31:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 18 Mar 2018 23:10:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-20"}
